Sentencas: Ba1-xSrxCo0.8Fe0.2O3-delta (BSCF)(0 <= x <= 1) composite oxides were prepared and tested as cathodes for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs) both in the absence and presence Of CO2.
Titulo: Investigation of Ba1-xSrxCo0.8Fe0.2O3-δ as cathodes for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells both in the absence and presence of CO2

Sentencas: It is found that the BSCF cathodes in the whole range of strontium (loping levels show promising performance at 500-600 degrees C in the absence Of CO2, among which the SrCo0.8Fe0.2O3-delta (SCF) cathode gives the highest power density while BaCo0.8Fe0.2O3-delta (BCF) cathode shows the lowest performance.
Titulo: Investigation of Ba1-xSrxCo0.8Fe0.2O3-δ as cathodes for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells both in the absence and presence of CO2

Sentencas: The impedance analysis reveals that both the ohmic resistance and polarization resistance of the fuel cell increases when the strontium content decreases.
Titulo: Investigation of Ba1-xSrxCo0.8Fe0.2O3-δ as cathodes for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells both in the absence and presence of CO2

Sentencas: It is believed that the microstructure and electrical conductivity simultaneously affect the process of oxygen reduction.
Titulo: Investigation of Ba1-xSrxCo0.8Fe0.2O3-δ as cathodes for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells both in the absence and presence of CO2

Sentencas: The presence of CO2 deteriorates the BSCF performance by adsorbing on the cathode surface and thus obstructing the oxygen surface exchange reaction.
Titulo: Investigation of Ba1-xSrxCo0.8Fe0.2O3-δ as cathodes for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells both in the absence and presence of CO2

Sentencas: The CO2 exerts a more intense influence on BSCF with higher barium content.
Titulo: Investigation of Ba1-xSrxCo0.8Fe0.2O3-δ as cathodes for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells both in the absence and presence of CO2
